summary: The implementation successfully addresses all four requirements. The scheduling page with comprehensive form validation and all required fields was created (REQ-16), the Schedule Service navigation link was added to the header between Contact and phone number (REQ-17), the logo was replaced with the user-provided image file (REQ-18), and Schedule Service CTA buttons were added to both HeroSection and CTABlock components (REQ-19). All acceptance criteria appear to be met based on the diff evidence.
